    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《铜刀银剑》官方QQ交流群：2667165420 欢迎建议~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315770/extras/5d376737523096cb5071cb152b7e640e.avif?t=1772295086\" width=800 height=178 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  江湖‘刺’榜第三，黑道成名已久的‘铜刀客’滋生心魔，饱受梦魇折磨的他接受了人生中最重要的任务————前往京师，借献“人杰玺”之事刺杀奸相 从此便由魔入正，做救民于水火的正道英雄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  铜刀客与艺妓银蝶儿一起启程，从荆湖北路出发前往京师，这迢迢旅途，不知有多少凶险，又有多少温香？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  本游戏是一款视觉小说，通过点击鼠标，阅读浮现的文字进而推动剧情。以江湖的爱恨情仇和家国大义为主线。讲述一个经典又不失新意的武侠故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315770/extras/b79996b2b29c5cf6d5e58a5fd9d374c9.avif?t=1772295086\" width=760 height=3747 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315770/extras/0b70a15518472be365df17c593078426.avif?t=1772295086\" width=800 height=178 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主策划：轮呐德</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主催：蟒魂</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧本创作：对硝基甲苯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美术：蟒魂</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐：Ember 木南</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UI：E Cloudy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总监：天羽却 </p>",
